OL,3,C'Sick' anti-corruption police officer
OL,4,Csuspended over double jobbing claim
OL,6,FUTV can reveal a senior police officer
OL,7,Fhas been suspended, accused of double
OL,8,Fjobbing for a legacy body.
OL,10,FThe officer - whose identity is known
OL,11,Fto us, but we can't reveal because of
OL,12,Flegal reasons - worked for the unit
OL,13,Fwhich investigates alleged misconduct
OL,14,Fwithin the PSNI.
OL,16,FHe was signed off from that job on the
OL,17,Fsick, but it's claimed he was well
OL,18,Fenough to take up another role with
OL,19,Fthe new legacy body the Independent
OL,20,FCommission For Reconciliation and
OL,21,FInformation Retrevial (ICRIR).
