OL,3,C'Sick' anti-corruption police officer
OL,4,Csuspended over double jobbing claim
OL,6,FBut when the top brass here found out
OL,7,Fwhat he was allegedly up to, he was
OL,8,Fimmediately suspended.
OL,10,FTwo investigations - one internal, the
OL,11,Fother criminal - which is about to be
OL,12,Fopened.
OL,14,FPSNI Deputy Chief Constable Bobby
OL,15,FSingleton said: "When it comes to any
OL,16,Fform of misconduct that flies in the
OL,17,Fface of the values of the
OL,18,Forganisation, of course we're
OL,19,Fdisappointed about it.
